global.title: CHOOSE YOUR TYPE OF STOKKE® XPLORY® ATHLEISURE

productIDs.description:
Our designers have taken the best elements of activewear to outfit Stokke® Xplory® Athleisure with a dynamic new look, and increased functionality. A nod to performance wear, grey is the primary colour to anchor the look. Traditional, and with broad appeal, it provides the ideal canvas for vibrant accents that express the energising spirit of Athleisure. Breathable, with pops of fresh Marina Blue or Coral, the technical fabrics have been carefully selected for their wicking and quick-dry properties.

To keep everything you and your baby need securely stowed, we've included a shopping bag with coordinating Marina Blue or Coral detailing.This unique stroller is available with a silver or black chassis and a carry cot option.

Stokke® Xplory® Athleisure with black chassis includes a matching black cup holder.

accessories.description: For attachment on chassis handle. Compatible with Stokke® Xplory® chassis with serial number 331324 and higher and with all Stokke® Crusi™, Stokke® Trailz™ and Stokke® Scoot™ chassis. For Stokke® Xplory® from serial number 127390 to 331323 an adaptor is necessary and can be purchased separately.

Our genuine Sheepskin lining is a perfect fit for our strollers and your baby. Sourced from New Zealand and Australian flocks, it is natural, comfortable and stylish.
 
People often think that sheepskin is only for keeping warm, fortunately, this is simply not true. Due to the hollow fibers of the wool, pure sheepskin has a natural breathing quality that helps to maintain a steady body temperature for your little one in all types of weather. It gives plush, cushioning support and feels soft next to your baby´s delicate skin.
 
A brush for freshening and reshaping the lining is included.

 
Adapted to use with 5 point harness.

accessories.productName: Stokke® iZi Go Modular™ by BeSafe®
accessories.description: Weighing in at only 4.4 kg, the lightweight Stokke® iZi Go Modular™ by BeSafe®  baby car seat is easy to install and carry. The seat features an ergonomically designed carrying handle, adjustable 5-point safety harness, an integrated canopy with built in ventilation and plush padding for exceptional comfort and protection. Rest assured that your baby is safely and comfortably seated for your journeys together; the car seat is developed by trusted Norwegian car seat manufacturer, BeSafe®, which has provided Scandinavian safety since 1963.

accessories.description: Let your stroller grow with your family. The Stokke® Xplory® Sibling Board allows your toddler to ride right alongside his or her sibling. Designed for children approximately 2 years to 44 lbs / 20kg, the Sibling Board connects to the Stokke® Xplory® stroller and remains attached when the stroller is folded. Keep your family close with the Stokke® Xplory® Sibling Board.

Suitable from newborn to approximately 12 months, the Stokke® Down Sleeping Bag measures 71 cm long. Made of down and lined with soft fleece, it has concealed flaps for the 5 point harness of your stroller. This universal accessory fits all brands of strollers and comes in colors to match our stroller collection as well as the Stokke® Xplory® Winter Kit.

accessories.description: Traveling with your children can be one of life’s richest experiences. The Stokke® PramPack™ was designed so that you can simply enjoy the journey whilst we ensure that your pram arrives safe and sound. Airline approved, the Stokke® PramPack™ fits almost any pram Once you arrive, simply roll the Stokke® PramPack™ up for easy storage. Simple. Bon Voyage!

Stokke® Fleece Sleeping Bag is made of soft, comfortable fleece material.
With a timeless design, the Sleeping bag can easily be mixed and matched with other Stokke® stroller accessories.
Gives your child shelter and protection against the cold. Practical and easy to open and close without disturbing the child.

For Winter, we have designed this season's most functional and beautiful outerwear… for your Stokke® stroller. The Winter Kit is a stylish way to keep your baby warm when temperatures drop. Your child will stay snug and protected from cold weather and wind, while enjoying the wonders of winter. We have been thinking of you as well; warm mittens that attach to the stroller handle with genuine sheepskin rims and soft fleece lining keep your hands toasty during your strolls together. The Winter Kit Collection for the seat of Stokke® Crusi™, Stokke® Trailz™ and the Seat and Carry Cot of Stokke® Xplory® includes sleek quilted detailing and is available in Pearl White, Onyx Black and brand new Bronze Brown. The textiles have a subtle shine for a sophisticated look. Our designers have carefully coordinated absolutely everything you need to stay warm and look hot this winter!

accessories.description:
The Summer Kit has been developed with your baby in mind to protect their sensitive skin on sunny days. Thoughtful details such as extra ventilation zippers for optimal air flow and fabrics with UPF 50+ protection keep your baby cool even in warm temperatures. The smart sunsail shades your baby from direct sunlight so that they won´t feel hot or uncomfortable while they rest in the shade. Summer Kit also includes a unique terry cloth seat cover to absorb moisture for cooling and comfort. The soft terry cloth cover comes in soft, complementary colours to complete the look.

The pattern features flowers and animals on the interior that are sure to catch your baby´s eye. Sophisticated and subtle, the Summer Kit, with its whimsical pattern is the perfect way to keep your baby entertained during your summer strolls.  Use the animals and flowers to make up your own stories as you go.

accessories.productName: Stokke® iZi Go™ X1 by BeSafe®
accessories.description: Weighing in at only 4.2 kilos, the Stokke® iZi Go X1 by BeSafe® is easy to install and even easier to carry. This ultra light car seat includes an adjustable 5 point safety harness, an integrated sun canopy and plush padding for exceptional comfort and added protection. Best of all, Stokke® iZi Go X1 by BeSafe® can also be used as a pram seat with all Stokke® prams without the use of adaptors, it simply clicks right onto the chassis. Available in colours to match for superior styling. Stokke® iZi Go X1 by BeSafe® makes life's little transitions that much easier.

accessories.description:
Stokke Stroller blanket is a multi purposed, soft knitted, and breathable blanket. It helps to keep baby snug in cooler weather and coordinate perfectly with Stokke Stroller colour range. 

Made of 100% cotton. Stokke® textiles are Oeko-Tex® Standard 100, class 1 approved and certified free from hazardous substances with the latest research and technology, governing what’s best for your baby.

Please remember that blankets should not be placed over the opening of the stroller to allow proper ventilation and heat regulation for your child.
